<br>
Time:<br>
be at the toxxulia spires for 5:30 PM EST<br>
we will be porting up at 6<br>
** this should take us 3 to 4 hours to clear the island me thinks, if we get enough people at first **<br>
<br>
Strategy:<br>
I am looking for 5 to 6 groups of 50  people to help me with this. I have a corpse up there with a full set of keys on it already. I am going to have a necro go up to the 7th island and start a corpse summoning chain(as COTH does not work). You will be expected to die in a duel, no exp lost. Once summoned up to the isle you will be placed in a group and once everyone is buffed and ready, we will begin pulling. Most of the mobs will before us fairly easily, but there are gryphons up there that when pulled will be giving off a death touch(20,000 dmg, no pain is even felt). All mages who are expecting anything will be expected to take at least 1 or 2 depending on how many come up.<br>
<br>
Loot:<br>
I am reserving 1 crown of elemental mastery for myself! There is a chance for 0 to 3 crowns dropping when we hit the island. All other quest pieces will be randomed as usual and the need before greed rule does apply. The plane of sky has some interesting loot on it as well. It drops quest pieces which can be turned in on the 1st island for some pretty decent weapons and armor<br>
<br>
Other notes:<br>
There will be no /say allowed! There are different creatures that respond to different phrases and can kill the whole party off in one fell swoop. So all comments and everything will be limited to tells, shouts, and the channel. This also includes no hailing the mobs or npc's that may pop upon clearing the island.<br>
<br>
When you get to toxxulia forest there, please join chat channel lovebug please (thanks Rollen for helping me with these names <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->     )<br>
